<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>trnymạt rwḥyẗ</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- yā nab̊ʿa ạảf̊rāḥī ạl̊gẖanī̃̊
 muḥ̊yī tahānīhā
 yā maj̊da ạảyãạmī ạlsãnī̃̊
 sal̊way̱ layālīhā

[V2]
 2- fī ạlẓũl̊maẗi ạl̊quṣ̊way̱ matay̱
 luḥ̊ta ạb̊tadā faj̊rī
 mar̊ậka lilnãf̊si ạảtay̱
 biạlsẖãm̊si wāl̊bad̊ri

[V3]
 3- tuḍīʾu min̊ ḥaẘlī ạlsãmā
 ại̹dẖā badā rabĩy
 faqal̊bahu ạảray̱ kamā
 yaray̱ hūa qal̊bī

[V4]
 4- turīdu naf̊sī ʿin̊da dẖāk̊
 ạản̊ tat̊ruka ạldũn̊yā
 watar̊taqī ại̹lay̱ hunāk̊
 lilrãạḥaẗi ạl̊ʿul̊yā</lyrics>
<title>yạ nbʿ ạ̉frạḥy ạlgẖny</title>
</song>